  <brief_title>Amniotic Fluid Optical Density Determination as a Test for Assessment of Fetal Lung Maturity.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Amniotic Fluid Optical Density Determination Between 28 and 36 6/7 Weeks of Pregnancy and Its Relationship With the Diagnosis of Neonatal Respiratory Distress Syndrome.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
