  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the relationship between the result of amniotic fluid optical density between 26
      and 36 6/7 weeks of pregnancy and the risk of developing neonatal respiratory distress
      syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
